    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes an application programming interface and a corresponding protocol (MGCP) for controlling Voice over IP (VoIP) Gateways from external call control elements.  MGCP assumes a call control architecture where the call control "intelligence" is outside the gateways and handled by external call control elements.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
